There are no new missions, and it`s making http://anidb.net/ch111128 [Neku] nervous. http://anidb.net/ch111130 [Joshua], however, has his own agenda, and he wants Neku to lend him a hand. When the pair reunite with http://anidb.net/ch115344 [Hanekoma], a chance remark sparks a memory in Neku.
